The paper is about self-supervised learning methods for visual feature learning using deep neural networks. This topic falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the evaluation metrics and datasets used in this field, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the use of deep neural networks for self-supervised learning is a common technique in the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
